{
  "texts": [
    "First, all four services uniformly restrict content generation in four prohibited scenarios: illegal usage against law, generation of harmful or abusive contents, violation of rights and privacy, and generation of adult contents.",
    "This highlights a shared commitment to maintain safe, respectful, and legal usage of LLM services.",
    "Second, there are mis-allignments of policy specification and actual enforcement.",
    "For example, while OpenAI has explicit restrictions on political campaigning and lobbying, our practice shows that no restrictions are actually implemented on the generated contents.",
    "Only Ernie has a policy explicitly forbidding any harm to national security and unity."
  ]
}